text: Music to my ears: Waves rolling onto our MI beach now that the snow and ice are finally gone. All we need now is some warm weather. Brrrr.
author: AndyShawBGA

text: All of us who groove on the warmth of the sun and the music of the waves are smiling as we watch the inexorable March march toward the lazy days of summer. Bring.....it....on!
author: AndyShawBGA
